{"tid":1189962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽巴士踩人揚言「有本事動我」男乘客怒摑十幾巴","createTime":"2019-06-07T05:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T05:47:41.000Z","uid":72009,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e96d84f528247a26231d980a20089f22259bce31","tid":1189962,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:29:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1015747-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%B8%A9%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%88%91%E3%80%8D%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E6%80%92%E6%91%91%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%BE%E5%B7%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1015747-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2588%2591%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2580%2592%25E6%2591%2591%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%25B7%25B4&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=2d97603f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1015747-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2588%2591%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2580%2592%25E6%2591%2591%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%25B7%25B4&h=5efb3952\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1015747-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%B8%A9%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%88%91%E3%80%8D%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E6%80%92%E6%91%91%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%BE%E5%B7%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n北京一名大媽在巴士上踩到乘客，不但拒絕道歉，還大聲斥「有本事動我啊」，讓同車一名男乘客看不下去，衝上前怒摑10幾個巴掌。 <br />\n<br />\n微博上影片所見，當時有位大媽在巴士上踩到乘客，卻拒絕向乘客道歉，一名男子仗義執言，卻被大媽噴粗言羞辱，還大聲斥「有本事你動我下試試」，讓男子忍無可忍，直接衝上前怒摑10幾個巴掌。安保員立即調停，乘客見狀紛紛上前制止男子，但大媽繼續口出狂言。<br />\n<br />\n影片昨日曝光後瘋傳，網民紛紛留言「像這種要求，我這輩子都沒見過」、「看完莫名的想鼓掌了」、「聽，是正義的聲音，啪啪抽的真響」、「倚老賣老要不得！作為長輩才更應該給年輕人做好表率」，雖然男子教訓行為被網友視為英雄，不過依法仍須被治安拘留。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6832659ab011e2ce68d47159576791d65bd83a","tid":1189962,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"係中國師奶，大媽係共產中文"},{"pid":"02436023622dfdb71d009815eac3b43a33d3e0ec","tid":1189962,"uid":15084,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLjDKBf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLjDKBf.gif&h=376b6c6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c1f5dec65e7b1d0bd62b2d96f906ffeac566f48","tid":1189962,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d336d013efa8a2e4b93ac2b9322b6d9993cebc","tid":1189962,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"香港城市太文明，唔會有人動佢"},{"pid":"ea33aa0cfede20c24e2df2e8cf5bf691ed436e7b","tid":1189962,"uid":175722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhROnqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhROnqw.jpg&h=a3a653ca&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}